{{location map~|North Korea|label=平壤|position=right|lat=39.063457|long=125.789200|region=KP-01|mark=Blue pog.svg}}
{{location map~|North Korea|label=會寧| position=left|lat=42.537967|long=129.935517|region=KP-09}}}}
'''會寧集中營'''（{{kor|名=北|k=회령 정치범수용소}}），又稱「22號營房」，是[[朝鮮|朝鮮]]用作關押[[政治犯|政治犯]]的集中營之一，位於朝鮮東北部[[中華人民共和國|中]][[朝鲜|朝]]邊境附近的[[會寧市|會寧市]]山谷。大約可容纳五万人勞改。
該集中營已於2012年後關閉，理由是會寧集中營太接近中國和俄羅斯的邊境[[圖們江|圖們江]]，為防止犯人逃離朝鮮故關閉之。

== 簡述 ==
会宁集中营于1965年在[[朝鲜|朝鲜]][[咸镜北道|咸镜北道]]的会宁市修建，80、90年代又扩建到会宁市的[[仲峰|仲峰]]（朝鲜语：중봉）。在90年代<ref name="nkdb105"/>，该集中营所关押的犯人人数急剧增加，而当时[[咸镜北道|咸镜北道]]的其他三个集中营已经关闭，其犯人被转移到了这所集中营。<ref>{{citation | title= Political Prison Camps in North Korea Today | chapter= 2.1.2 History of Each Political Prison Camp (p. 72 - 75) | work= Database Center for North Korean Human Rights | date= July 15, 2011 | url= http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | accessdate= June 20, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130228031922/http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | archivedate= 2013年2月28日 }}</ref>而被关押进来的人大多數是因為批評[[朝鮮勞動黨|朝鮮勞動黨]]或領導人[[金正日|金正日]]而因言獲罪的，与被断定在政治上不可靠的（如韓戰回國戰俘，基督徒，從日本回流僑民）。集中營同時亦接收[[脫北者|脫北者]]的家屬或受牽連人士，由大約1000名警衛和500至600名行政人员进行控制。

==内部环境==
曾经在会宁集中营工作的狱卒[[安明哲|安明哲]]（由《朝鲜月刊》Monthly Chosun报道）表示，集中营内部的生活环境极其恶劣，甚至威胁生命<ref name="mcho">{{cite web | title= The testimony of An Myong-chol, an ex-guard at a political prisoners' camp in North Korea | work= Monthly Chosun Ilbo | url= http://monthly.chosun.com/client/dataroom/databoardread.asp?idx=9&cPage=5&table=dataroom | accessdate= June 20, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022224821/http://monthly.chosun.com/client/dataroom/databoardread.asp?idx=9&cPage=5&table=dataroom | archivedate= 2013年10月22日 }}</ref>。他回忆，初次到这个集中营时感到一种难以名状的震惊：这里的犯人就好像是骨瘦如材、衣衫褴褛的[[骷髅|骷髅]]和虫豸<ref name = "hrnk"/><ref>{{cite web | title= Typical Appearance of Prisoners | work= Daily NK, November 16, 2005 | url= http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=375 | accessdate= June 26, 2012 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160326133334/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=375 | archive-date= 2016-03-26 | dead-url= yes }}</ref>。这名狱卒估计，狱中大约有30%的犯人都曾被实施[[酷刑|酷刑]]和[[虐待|虐待]]，如割耳朵、碾碎眼球、掏空鼻腔，还有被鞭子或[[刑具|刑具]]抽打而在脸上留下的疤痕。还有大约2,000名犯人被[[截肢|截肢]]，但就算是杵拐杖的[[残疾人|残疾人]]也必须参加劳动<ref name="mcho2000">{{citation | title= The testimony of An Myong-chol, an ex-guard at a political prisoners' camp in North Korea | chapter= 2,000 Inmates Missing Arms or Legs | work= Monthly Chosun Ilbo | date= March 1995 | url= http://monthly.chosun.com/client/dataroom/databoardread.asp?idx=9&cPage=5&table=dataroom | accessdate= June 20, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022224821/http://monthly.chosun.com/client/dataroom/databoardread.asp?idx=9&cPage=5&table=dataroom | archivedate= 2013年10月22日 }}</ref>。集中营每日会给每名犯人发放180克的[[谷物|谷物]]，但几乎吃不到蔬果和肉类食品<ref>{{citation | title= Political Prison Camps in North Korea Today | chapter= 4.1.2 Food Rations (p. 362) | work= Database Center for North Korean Human Rights | date= July 15, 2011 | url= http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | accessdate= June 26, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130228031922/http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | archivedate= 2013年2月28日 }}</ref>，而肉食的唯一来源竟是在狱中出没的[[老鼠|老鼠]]，[[蛇|蛇]]和[[癞蛤蟆|癞蛤蟆]]<ref name = "hrnk"/><ref>{{cite web| title= Prisoners Catch Rats For Survival| work= Daily NK, November 25, 2005| url= http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=395| accessdate= June 26, 2012| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160529145122/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=395| archive-date= 2016-05-29| dead-url= yes}}</ref>。每年约有1,500到2,000人会因为[[营养不良|营养不良]]，[[器官衰竭|器官衰竭]]而死亡，其中大多数是少年儿童，但囚犯总人数是保持不变的。每年[[朝鲜|朝鲜]]当局会送来约1,500到2,000名囚犯来这里服刑<ref>{{citation | title= The testimony of An Myong-chol, an ex-guard at a political prisoners' camp in North Korea | chapter= Death Rules Each Day | work= Monthly Chosun Ilbo | date= March 1995 | url= http://monthly.chosun.com/client/dataroom/databoardread.asp?idx=9&cPage=5&table=dataroom | accessdate= June 20, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022224821/http://monthly.chosun.com/client/dataroom/databoardread.asp?idx=9&cPage=5&table=dataroom | archivedate= 2013年10月22日 }}</ref>。集中营里，[[儿童|儿童]]只能接受最基础的教育<ref>{{citation | title= Political Prison Camps in North Korea Today | chapter= 4.5.3 Mobilized Labor for Children (p. 450 - 451) | work= Database Center for North Korean Human Rights | date= July 15, 2011 | url= http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | accessdate= June 26, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130228031922/http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | archivedate= 2013年2月28日 }}</ref>，六岁后就会被安排任务开始劳动，如到田里收菜，给谷物剥壳，-{晒}-稻米等，但是获得的食物很少，每天只有约180克，这对成長期中的儿童来说远远不够。因此，很多儿童都活不过10岁<ref>{{citation | title= Political Prison Camps in North Korea Today | chapter= 4.5.3 Mobilized Labor for Children (p. 443 - 444) | work= Database Center for North Korean Human Rights | date= July 15, 2011 | url= http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | accessdate= June 26, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130228031922/http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | archivedate= 2013年2月28日 }}</ref>。年长的犯人和其他人一样每天都会做同样强度的劳作<ref>{{citation | title= Political Prison Camps in North Korea Today | chapter= 4.4.4 Minimum Age for Labor and Labor of the Old and the Weak (p. 423) | work= Database Center for North Korean Human Rights | date= July 15, 2011 | url= http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | accessdate= June 26, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130228031922/http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | archivedate= 2013年2月28日 }}</ref>，而身患重病的犯人经检疫之后就会被遗弃，自生自灭。<ref>{{cite web| title= Patients Quarantined, Abandoned and Left to Die| work= Daily NK, November 29, 2005| url= http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=402| accessdate= June 26, 2012| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160529145129/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=402| archive-date= 2016-05-29| dead-url= yes}}</ref>

不具有婚姻关系的囚犯居住在100人同时起居的集体工棚内。为奖励劳动积极分子，集中营允许家庭成员一起居住在一个单独的小房间内，但不提供[[自来水|自来水]]<ref>{{citation | title= Political Prison Camps in North Korea Today | chapter= 4.1.1 Housing Facilities (p. 352) | work= Database Center for North Korean Human Rights | date= July 15, 2011 | url= http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | accessdate= June 26, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130228031922/http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | archivedate= 2013年2月28日 }}</ref>。而供住宿的牢房状况很糟糕，墙壁是土坯的，并且有很多裂缝<ref>{{cite web | title=Prisoners’ Sheds in the Detention Settlement | work=Daily NK, November 15, 2005 | url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=372 | accessdate=June 20, 2012 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419142232/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=372 | archive-date=2016-04-19 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在其中的所有犯人都要共用数个肮脏、拥挤的马桶来排便。<ref>{{cite web | title=Communal Toilet For All Prisoners | work=Daily NK, November 28, 2005 | url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=400 | accessdate=June 20, 2012 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419134354/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=400 | archive-date=2016-04-19 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

集中营内的犯人每天都要干很沉重的农活，或在矿点、[[工厂|工厂]]里劳作，工作时间是从早上5点到晚上8点（冬季到晚上7点），<ref name="Chosun"/>还伴有思想政治教育和自我批评会议<ref>{{citation | title= Political Prison Camps in North Korea Today | chapter= 3.2.5 Discipline Session, Ideology Study and Lectures (p. 239) | work= Database Center for North Korean Human Rights | date= July 15, 2011 | url= http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | accessdate= June 26, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130228031922/http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | archivedate= 2013年2月28日 }}</ref>，而犯人唯一的假日就是元旦<ref>{{citation | title= Political Prison Camps in North Korea Today | chapter= 4.4.3 Break Time and Holidays (p. 416) | work= Database Center for North Korean Human Rights | date= July 15, 2011 | url= http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | accessdate= June 26, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130228031922/http://nkdb.org/bbs1/data/publication/Political_Prison_Camp_in_North_Korea_Today.pdf | archivedate= 2013年2月28日 }}</ref>。犯人所在的矿点并不具备有效的安全措施来保障人身安全，所以几乎每天都会有人遇险死亡。他们仅仅用最原始的劳作工具来工作，如铲子，并且被强迫劳动到筋疲力竭为止。就算矿点发生火灾或者出口[[塌方|塌方]]被堵死，也没人会来营救这些被困的犯人<ref>{{cite web | title= Prisoners Abandoned in a Collapsing Mine | work= Daily NK, December 30, 2005 | url= http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=465 | accessdate= June 20, 2012 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160419114047/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02600&num=465 | archive-date= 2016-04-19 | dead-url= yes }}</ref>。而据“朝鲜人权数据库”（Database Center for North Korean Human Rights）的资料，集中营把犯人的尸体堆到货车上，丢进熔炉焚化<ref name="nkdb187"/>。煤炭被运到[[清津市|清津市]]发电厂用于发电，而生产的食物则供应到[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国国家安全保卫部|朝鲜民主主义人民共和国国家安全保卫部]]，或者在首都[[平壤|平壤]]及朝鲜的其他地区进行销售。<ref>{{citation | title= The testimony of An Myong-chol, an ex-guard at a political prisoners' camp in North Korea | chapter= Enormous Slave Factories | work= Monthly Chosun Ilbo | date= March 1995 | url= http://monthly.chosun.com/client/dataroom/databoardread.asp?idx=9&cPage=5&table=dataroom | accessdate= June 20, 2012 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022224821/http://monthly.chosun.com/client/dataroom/databoardread.asp?idx=9&cPage=5&table=dataroom | archivedate= 2013年10月22日 }}</ref><ref name="nkdb333"/>

== 虐囚指控 ==
不少國際傳媒報導均稱該集中營存在不少有關[[人權|人權]]侵犯的案件，包括將囚犯投進[[毒氣室|毒氣室]]作化學實驗，供監獄人員觀察，當中部分指控與前會寧集中營負責人權革（{{lang|ko|권혁}}）有關。

